snippet.title: King Arthur: Legends Rise - Story Trailer | Summer Game Fest 2023
snippet.description:
Check out this new trailer for King Arthur: Legends Rise, an upcoming squad RPG, received a story trailer today. It is available to pre-order on mobile and PC platforms.

#GameTrailers #SoG #Gaming
